<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• صَنفر الخشبَ:</span> حكَّه بالصَّنْفرة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>